<paragraph base="F32570040" principles="yes" id="IFRS09_5.2.2"><paranum> 5.2.2</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 9"/><data name="paranum" value="5.2.2"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS09_P0295">An entity shall apply the impairment requirements in <xref base="F41732368" href="IFRS09_g5.5.1-5.5.20.dita#IFRS09_g5.5.1-5.5.20/IFRS09_g5.5.1-5.5.20_TI" id="IFRS09_X0432">Section 5.5</xref> to financial assets that are measured at <xref base="F32570588" href="IFRS09_APPA.dita#IFRS09_APPA/IFRS09_P0666">amortised cost<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0013"/></ph></xref> in accordance with <xref base="F41732369" href="IFRS09_4.1.2.dita#IFRS09_4.1.2" id="IFRS09_X0433">paragraph 4.1.2</xref> and to financial assets that are measured at fair value through other comprehensive income in accordance with <xref base="F41732370" href="IFRS09_4.1.2A.dita#IFRS09_4.1.2A" id="IFRS09_X0434">paragraph 4.1.2A</xref>.</p></body></paragraph>